vote.title: Authorize the sale of one 1999 John Deere Loader & Backhoe and one 2001 Caterpillar Track Dozer through a public auction ending May 18, 2020 to Gonzalez Truck & Equipment Inc. in the amount of $21,050.00 and Victor Ramirez in the amount of $43,025.00, highest bidders - Revenue:  Equipment and Fleet Management Fund ($36,571.25), Dallas Water Utilities Fund ($17,892.50), and Express Business Center Fund ($9,611.25)
